  {
    "id": "Ugwfds9brhE3mPHrlqZ4AaABAg",
    "author": "@tmathison66",
    "author_channel_id": "UCuS8wXYESysVZEJFU1YMeHQ",
    "text": "I rather like the fun you are having with bamboo. My worries stem from battery placement/lack of metal skid plate.\n\nBatteries that close to the ground and shielded only by HDPE are only a random rock away from becoming a sulfuric acid spreader - or lithium or whatever.",
    "likes": 1,
    "published_at": "2021-07-06T18:06:05Z",
    "reply_count": 3,
    "replies": [
      {
        "id": "Ugwfds9brhE3mPHrlqZ4AaABAg.9PTC3H1z7fm9PTF-tazzhq",
        "author": "@ThinkingandTinkering",
        "author_channel_id": "UC4AkVj-qnJxNtKuz3rkq16A",
        "text": "to be honest mate - I think you might be over worrying there - this does 5mph if you are lucky it takes much more force than that to break a battery case",
        "likes": 1,
        "published_at": "2021-07-06T18:31:50Z"
      },
