        "author_channel_id": "UCuS8wXYESysVZEJFU1YMeHQ",
        "text": "There's way more clearance under a car because they need to be able to leave parking lots. It's the back end of the battery that looks like it only has about two inches of clearance. Moving it forward would help immensely because of the angle. I don't remember if that was possible. Another option is not having the rear wheel straight out the back. Lower it a little and the problem is solved another way.",
        "likes": 0,
        "published_at": "2021-07-07T16:26:56Z"
      }
    ]
